#---8---CHECK PRIME

n=int(input("Enter a number:"))
if n<2:
    print("Not prime")
elif all(n%i != 0 for i in range(2, int(n**0.5)+1)):
    print("Prime")
else:
    print("Not prime")

OUTPUT

Enter a number:91
Prime

============================

